      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to be sharing this beauty with you. This car is an absolute dream\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it's spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a real gem that\u2019s been pampered its whole life, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
