    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an immaculate, collector-tier E46 M3. This S54-powered icon features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with a documented Vanos overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The naturally aspirated 3.2L power plant maintains factory compression across all cylinders, paired with a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are preserved via OEM+ dampers and factory-spec bushings, ensuring the original longitudinal and lateral load characteristics remain razor-sharp. Zero oxidation, factory-correct paint thickness, and a showroom-spec cabin define this investment-grade example.",
