      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a flawless deep-gloss finish, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the original factory scent lingers, and every piece of technology functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a chassis that has never seen rain or inclement weather, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in its purest, most pristine form.",
